# CommonMark container blocks converter in C

> Implement a from-scratch C program that converts CommonMark Markdown (lists and block quotes subset) to HTML via stdin/stdout. The binary must build via make at /app/workspace/md2html and match reference HTML on visible and held-out test cases.

---

## Task Configuration

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| Difficulty | hard |
| Category | programming |
| Agent Timeout | 7200s |
| Verifier Timeout | 600s |
| Internet Access | Disabled |
| CPUs / Memory | 2 / 4096 MB |

